
             THANKS - List of credits for Niji

I owe these people/groups my thanks for help with Niji. Thanks, guys!

- apoelstra              Providing input on getting the internal structures to work
- Benny Baumann          Several ideas and optimizations in GeSHi, initiator of Niji
- Christian Weiske       Several optimizations in the Parser of GeSHi
- Nigel McNie            Initial work on GeSHi, which Niji is a port of

Also I want to thank everybody who contributed to Niji by providing input of any
kind to its predecessor GeSHi.

Do you want your name in here? Help me out! Make a language file, or suggest a new
feature, or make a plugin for Niji for some other software, then tell me about it!
